             was indicted for <rs id="t17850511-38-off214" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850511-38-off214" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850511-38-off214" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17850511-38-victim450" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Squires
                        <interp inst="t17850511-38-victim450" type="surname" value="Squires"></interp>
