                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850511-38-defend448 t17850511-38-punish220"></join>
               confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
